features: 【Multifunctional & Convenient】This file cabinet with 4 storage shelves and 2 file drawers, is perfect to keep files, documents, paper, books and office supplies organized in your office, living room or study room. It can be fixed beside or under the desk, making it easy to reach and freeing up workspace.

【Large Storage Space】With large surface (43.3” L x15.7” W), the lateral filing cabinet can hold printer, fax machine or other office machines. The 3 cubicles stack your books, decors for easy access and the large shelf can store lever arch files. Two drawers for hanging A4 and letter-size files, everything finds its place and keeps your workstation neat.

【Move Without Noise】Five 360°rotating wheels design makes it can move smoothly and silently without scratching the floor. Two lockable casters keep the mobile file cabinet stable in position and the fifth caster on the bottom enhances stability and prevents collapse. An excellent partner to accompany you for a long time.

【Solid Construction】Premium MDF board makes this printer cabinet water, scratch, wear-resistant and easily clean. Constructed of 0.59” thick panels, this solidly constructed printer cabinet with evenly distributed maximum weight capacity of 200lbs.

【Easy Assembly & Service】Assembly step by step with detailed instructions, and the necessary tools and hardware is also included. If there is any question, feel free to contact us. We provide 18 months of quality assurance and friendly customer service.
body.description: Tribesigns 2 Drawers Large File Cabinet Printer Stand with Storage Shelves Say goodbye to the messy stacks of paper and lost documents from now. A rolling file cabinet with a modern look, 2 large drawers, 4 open shelves, and 5 sturdy wheels, and a great way to free up your workspace while inviting touch of industrial charisma to your home office. Match the heights of many desks to create a spacious feeling and extended workspace when placed near or under the desk. Constructed of high-quality MDF board, the filing cabinet fends off scratches and stains, easy for daily maintenance. With large desktop and open shelving, this office cabinet can store anything you need at arms reaches away. ​Two file drawers with wooden handles pull open to reveal space inside for A4 or letter-size documents. It's founded atop casters, so you can move it from room to room with ease without scratching your floor.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Appearance is perfect.
reviews.reviewText: I thought this was worth the money. It's stylish and fits my office perfectly. I love that it has wheels to move around. I bought 2 of them and it fits my needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice but challenging
reviews.reviewText: I hought this item to help condense and organize our office. It arrived just fine, no scratches, and looks nice. My husband is super handy so putting this together was his jam. However, when we got to the file drawers came the challenge. The first drawer doesn't close completely and we can't figure out why. The second drawer he had trouble with the rails not lining up with the screw holes. Even using a magnetic screw driver he had a terrible time lining the rail up to put the screw in. He finally got it in but both drawers do not close flush to the cabinet but they don't look terrible they do seem to lock in place when pushed in, but they aren't flush. I liked the style and I figured if this one goes well I would.biy another one, so I'm still thinking.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good for the price
reviews.reviewText: Easy enough to put together and comes with extra bits. Assembled alone in under 2 hours and unfocused on the task. Tip: pull the rail tab down to unlock. The arrow in the instructions look like you need to push in on the rail, but that's not it. Also, the instructions state clearly on the 2nd page to not use a gun to construct this unit. Sound advice.

reviews.reviewText: What a piece of crap!!! poor quality products used to manufacture this OVERLY EXPENSIVE inferior trash, and when you think you can put some books on it, stand by!! The wheels are buckling under the weight of 5 books, the drawers will no longer close because the entire thing is bending like a pretzel.BUYER BEWARE - DON'T WASTE YOUR MONEY!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This was my 4th and final piece to put together. The desk and side piece, and tall hutchy thing were the other ones. All were long to do, but I followed directions following the pictures, and figuring out how they fit together. I am a 77 year old woman and put all 4 pieces together and the drawers work, doors open and everything looks great. So Thank you Tribesign. LOVE LOVE your furniture.

reviews.reviewTitle: Cheap poor quality compared to picture!
reviews.reviewText: Came in a million pieces same as IKEA quality with compressed wood. Very disappointed in the product and not worth the high price. 🙁 Asked for a refund and seller is asking for everything to be in the original state in all its packaging... how are we supposed to know it is poor quality before we start putting it together? Sad and will question buying online from Amazon for these types of products in the future. Poor customer service.
